    "name": "BirdsBorough : Town of Alchemy",
    "steam_appid": 2107130,
    "required_age": "16",
    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2107130/extras/905ef5003c69ca71987adde3c0739ea7.avif?t=1730397951\" width=600 height=112 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >*THIS GAME IS NO LONGER SUPPORTED, unfortunately this game did not receive the funding we needed to continue working on it and bring it to the quality we wanted. We appreciate everyone who supported this project and we're still proud of our first commercial release. BirdsBorough has been made free for anyone who enjoys the game or is curious to continue playing.*</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >After mysterious events a run-down potion shop has found it's way into your possession! The people of BirdsBorough have many unique problems for you to solve but you can create just as many unique potions brewed with various properties and powers. As you grow close to the people of BirdsBorough you may learn more secrets of this mysterious town you find yourself.... </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Combine 27 unique potion effects </strong>using a colour mixing alchemy system. All effects have can be combined by matching their effect colours in the cauldron and mixing them all together! All potions drastically effect those who drink them!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2107130/extras/2be1a1e7fa8ac558c1a932e39bcefff5.poster.avif?t=1730397951\" width=300 height=168 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2107130/extras/2be1a1e7fa8ac558c1a932e39bcefff5.webm?t=1730397951\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2107130/extras/2be1a1e7fa8ac558c1a932e39bcefff5.mp4?t=1730397951\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2107130/extras/779d61dd45c60ae63b85a39264c9d362.poster.avif?t=1730397951\" width=300 height=168 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2107130/extras/779d61dd45c60ae63b85a39264c9d362.webm?t=1730397951\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2107130/extras/779d61dd45c60ae63b85a39264c9d362.mp4?t=1730397951\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Solve NPCs unique problems</strong>, all NPCs have procedurally generated dialogue, so they'll always have something unique to say and unique problems to solve! It's up to you to figure out which potion would best help each NPC. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2107130/extras/84eefc3c2f98c68b6e9717929d4f2998.poster.avif?t=1730397951\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2107130/extras/84eefc3c2f98c68b6e9717929d4f2998.webm?t=1730397951\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2107130/extras/84eefc3c2f98c68b6e9717929d4f2998.mp4?t=1730397951\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Build your own potion store</strong> with various decorations and structures, in whatever way you want! As you collect funds from potion sales you'll be able to build you're own store in a large plot of land in the town, however you see fit, will you create an ominous monolith? A simple market stall? Or something else entirely! It's all up to you!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2107130/extras/64ad649889c3bd42723c37b9a2157d7d.poster.avif?t=1730397951\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2107130/extras/64ad649889c3bd42723c37b9a2157d7d.webm?t=1730397951\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2107130/extras/64ad649889c3bd42723c37b9a2157d7d.mp4?t=1730397951\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Grow and harvest multiple unique plants</strong>, from elder trees to death blooms, all of which will affect your potions in different ways!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2107130/extras/72c237d10b1b9d52f8b33649c1ba6116.avif?t=1730397951\" width=600 height=222 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2107130/extras/905ef5003c69ca71987adde3c0739ea7.avif?t=1730397951\" width=600 height=112 /></span></p>",
